function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	-- Grab the LevelARea
	S_HOLDOUT_LEVEL_AREA = Hydra.ActorGetLevelArea(idActorDetector)
	
	--Start the boss enounter
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyQueueStart(S_HOLDOUT_LEVEL_AREA)

	-- Start Spawns
	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tSpawners) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then
			Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, false)
		end
	end

	-- Delete the Trigger
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idActorDetector)
	
end
